# ğŸ’¡ Approach (EN)
1. Initialize `total = 0`.
2. Check every number `i` from `1` to `n`.
3. If `n % i == 0`, then `i` is a divisor â†’ add it to `total`.
4. Return `total`.

---

# ğŸ’¡ ì‚¬ê³  ê³¼ì • (KR)
