# ğŸ Python Solution (EN)

<details markdown="1">
<summary>Solution (My Approach)</summary>

```python
def solution(n):
    answer = []
    for i in range(1, n + 1):
        if n % i == 0:
            answer.append(i)
    return sum(answer)
```
</details> 

<details markdown="1"> <summary>Solution (Most Pythonic)</summary>

```sql
def solution(n):
    return sum(i for i in range(1, n + 1) if n % i == 0)
```
</details>

